
+-----------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Files included  | Description                                                         |
+-----------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------+
+-----------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------+
| port_knocker.c  | This kernel module implements a rudimentary port knocking feature   |
+-----------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Makefile        | Makefile that compiles kernel module `port_knocker.c`               |
+-----------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------+
| README          | Current file                                                        |
+-----------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------+



+---------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------+
| How to...                                         | Bash command                      |
+---------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------+
+---------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------+
| compile Linux kernel module `port_knocker.c`      | $ make                            |
+---------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------+
| clean directory                                   | $ make clean                      |
+---------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------+
| insert module packet_masker to kernel and specify | $ insmod port_knocker.ko \        |
| IPS to be masked                                  |   ip_addr=127.0.0.1 port=8080     |
+---------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------+
| create a server listening on port 8080            | $ ncat -l 8080                    |
+---------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------+
| scan port 8080                                    | nmap -p 8080-8080 localhost       |
+---------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------+
| remove module packet_masker from kernel           | $ rmmod port_knocker.ko           |
+---------------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------+
